                        <bsa>in <a>D. <l>Scharff</l></a> and <a>E. <l>Fairbairn Birtles</l></a>
                            (eds)</bsa>
                        <bst>From Instinct to Self</bst>, Vols <v>I</v> and <v>II</v>. Northvale,
                        NJ: <bp>Jason Aronson Inc</bp>.</be>
                </bib>
